= TTF_SetFontScriptName =

Set script per font.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int TTF_SetFontScriptName(TTF_Font *font, const char *script);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''font'''
|[[TTF_Font]] handle
|-
|'''script'''
|null terminated string of exactly 4 characters.
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns 0, or -1 if SDL_ttf is not compiled with HarfBuzz or invalid
parameter

== Remarks ==

It overrides the global script set with the deprecated [[TTF_SetScript]]().

